  Locus:
    Page: 229
    Verse: 16
Tags:
  - Happiness
---
Why do people worship God? For happiness. Why do people get married? For
happiness. Why do people divorce? For happiness. Everything is done in the
name of and for happiness. Still there is no happiness.
